4.24.25  8:22 am   this site is organized in a very interesting manner. how'd you do it

      first i tried to put everything in 1 place. but it felt like there were categories emerging. so i tried to categorize but the categories kept falling apart so i couldn't do it. but then still on one page i still kept wanting categories. so i would try it again but no the categories kept falling apart. and on like this for a while until eventually the desire for categories outweighed the worry for them being broken. and since then i've accepted the fact that we all love categories even though they are glaringly dysfunctional
